    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "（「お祝いありがとう！　お兄ちゃんも、また一年）\n（音楽活動頑張ってね。いつか共演したいな」……と）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "何をにやにやしているの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3666670721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "きゃあ！？　み、み、み、mihoさん！？\nべ、別に、にやにやなんてしていません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "格好も、随分と浮かれているわね\n……まぁ、誕生日だし、撮影でもあったんでしょうけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4700.000000000003,
          "startTime": 36.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ……これ、一応贈っておくわ\n興味を持ってるって聞いたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2266.666666699997,
          "startTime": 42.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ！　甘酒じゃないですか！\nもしかしてmihoさんがいつも飲んでるやつですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ありがとうございます。遙子さんも飲んでみたい\nって言ってましたし、今度、三人で一緒に飲みましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "なぜ甘酒で飲み会を開かないといけないのよ\nそれに遙子なんて、酔っていてもいなくても面倒なのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、お二人でよく居酒屋さんに行ってるみたい\nじゃないですか。あれ、ちょっといいなーって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "私が飲んでいると、勝手に遙子が合流してくるだけよ\n二人で居酒屋に行ったりはしていないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも、長瀬麻奈の親友らしいけれど、その親友を\n消そうとしていた私にベタベタする意味が分からない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "それは……詳しいことは私にも分かりませんけど……\nでも、遙子さんは、私に教えてくれたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "『周りにいる人は敵じゃない。同じ夢を目指す仲間よ』\nって。それが、遙子さんのスタンスみたいで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.2172965819,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "それに、何か通じるものがあるんじゃないですか？\n二人とも、同じ時期から活動してますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "私と遙子の共通点なんて、ほとんどないわよ\nあるとしたら……お互い、あの年の年末に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、分かんないなら、もっともっと仲良くなれば\nいいんですよ！　私も、二人には仲良くしてほしいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "私と遙子さんを取り持ってくれたのは\nmihoさんですし。今度は、私が間に入りますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、ちょうど寮で私の誕生日パーティーがあるので\nmihoさんも来て下さい。遙子さんの隣空けときます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8866.666666700014,
          "startTime": 150.5
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11200.000000000016,
          "startTime": 152.8333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 13166.666666700025,
          "startTime": 154.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "行かないわよ。それと、別に取り持ったつもりも……\nっ、袖を掴まないで。行かないって……ええい、離せ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6466.664530700001,
          "startTime": 157.5666645307
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8300.000000000011,
          "startTime": 159.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "ぐぬぬっ、離さぬ！\nそこをなんとか、美味しいご飯とお酒もありますから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "（今日は、一杯お祝いしてもらっちゃったわね）\n（私も、みんなも、変わらないところはあるけれど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "（少しずつ成長して、大人になれてる気がする）\n（いつか私も、先輩になる日が来るのかしら）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_03-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "（その時は、教えてあげなくちゃ。私が教わったことや）\n（私が教えられることを。私にとっての『アイドル』を）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}